版本升级步骤:
1. git clone/pull code

2. Update sys settings:
    modify settings.py, local_settings.py

3. update sql script
    cd /home/johnson/prod/projects/xizhi-server 
    运行: syncdb
    运行mysql升级脚本:update_script.sql

4. Run all unittest cases

5.Restart server:
   sudo service nginx restart
   sudo supervisorctl restart xizhi-server

6.测试验证
